  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\n\n2.17.1\n\n### What happened?\n\nI'm writing a test and .connect didn't change the msg.sender. More info: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/76919562/solidity-hardhat-testing-nft-transfer/76926496#76926496\r\n\r\n\n\n### Minimal reproduction steps\n\nHard to say because initially the first `.connect` worked (await token.connect(otherAccount.address)) but the subsequent lines of approve and transferFrom indicated that the second .connect didn't work.\n\n### Search terms\n\nconnect, test",
