    "body": "@Dobermensch `.connect` is not stateful ([docs](https://docs.ethers.org/v6/single-page/#BaseContract-connect)). That is, doing `token.connect(...)` won't change the address used by `token`. You have to either assign it to a new variable, or re-assign `token = token.connect(...)`.",
